data.description: Introducing this stunning like new two-story home, offering three spacious bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms. This masterpiece was designed to impress, boasting a perfect blend of style and functionality. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting floor plan that seamlessly provides an openness and tons of natural light. Upstairs, you'll find the tranquil primary bedroom, featuring a en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms, each with their own unique charm, share a well-appointed bathroom. Outside, the backyard, provides an extended covered patio with endless opportunities for outdoor activities and relaxation. With its modern design, thoughtful layout, and prime location, it offers everything you need for comfortable and stylish living.
